# Sandbox Tor configuration for the compose search profile.
# Tor is reachable only on the internal compose network.

SocksPort 0.0.0.0:9050 IsolateDestAddr IsolateDestPort
SocksPolicy accept 10.0.0.0/8
SocksPolicy accept 172.16.0.0/12
SocksPolicy accept 192.168.0.0/16
SocksPolicy reject *
NewCircuitPeriod 60
MaxCircuitDirtiness 30

ConnectionPadding 1
ReducedConnectionPadding 0

ControlPort 0
DNSPort 0

Log notice stdout
SafeLogging 1

DataDirectory /var/lib/tor

Sandbox 1
NoExec 1
